**Basic Endpoints & Features**

GET /api/books (all books):  
![][image1]  
[http://localhost:8080/api/books](http://localhost:8080/api/books)

 GET /api/books/{id} (book by ID):

![][image2][http://localhost:8080/api/books/1](http://localhost:8080/api/books/1)

POST /api/books (create book):  
![][image3]  
{  
  "title": "My Life Story",  
  "author": "Nevien Udugama",  
  "price": 242.99  
}

[http://localhost:8080/api/books](http://localhost:8080/api/books)

**Advanced Endpoints & Features**

PUT endpoint (update book): 

![][image4]  
[http://localhost:8080/api/books/1](http://localhost:8080/api/books/1)

PATCH endpoint (partial update):  
![][image5]  
{  
  "price": 29.99  
}  
[http://localhost:8080/api/books/1](http://localhost:8080/api/books/1)

DELETE endpoint (remove book):  
![][image6]  
[http://localhost:8080/api/books/1](http://localhost:8080/api/books/1)

GET endpoint with pagination:  
![][image7]  
[http://localhost:8080/api/books/paginated?page=0\&size=5](http://localhost:8080/api/books/paginated?page=0&size=5)

![][image8]  
[http://localhost:8080/api/books/paginated?page=1\&size=5](http://localhost:8080/api/books/paginated?page=1&size=5)

Advanced GET endpoint with filtering, sorting, and pagination combined in the valid order:  
![][image9]  
http://localhost:8080/api/books/advanced?title=java\&minPrice=30\&maxPrice=50\&sortBy=price\&order=asc\&page=0\&size=3  
![][image10]  
[http://localhost:8080/api/books/advanced?title=java\&minPrice=20\&maxPrice=50\&sortBy=price\&order=asc\&page=0\&size=5](http://localhost:8080/api/books/advanced?title=java&minPrice=20&maxPrice=50&sortBy=price&order=asc&page=0&size=5)

